Kenzo stood up right and gathered his will to explain the complicated
event.
"It's not the programming, she's been infested with some sort of
sentient alien parasite.  It called itself a vork.  And I'm afraid it
has entered her spark."  Kenzo explained best he could.   With that he
walked a bit closer.
"I'm afraid it will take quite a bit of skill, time and luck to get it
out."
